Name
Description




							Shmuel Lev


					
							Mr. Shmuel Lev serves as Co-Chairman of the Board at Analyst IMS Investment Management Services Ltd since August 02, 2009. Previously, Mr. Lev served as the Company's Chairman, Co-Chief Executive Officer and Director from August 01, 1985 to August 02, 2009. Mr. Lev has a Bachelor of Science degree in Industrial Engineering from the Technion-Israel Institute of Technology and a Masters of Business Administration degree from the Tel Aviv University.




							Ehud Shiloni


					
							Mr. Ehud Shiloni serves as Co-Chairman of the Board at Analyst IMS Investment Management Services Ltd since August 02, 2009. Previously, Mr. Shiloni served as the Company's Co-Chief Executive Officer and Director from April 17, 1986 to August 02, 2009. Mr. Shiloni has a Bachelor of Science degree in Industrial Engineering and Management Sciences from the Technion - Israel Institute of Technology.




							Itzhak Shenidovski


					
							Mr. Itzhak Shenidovski serves as Chief Executive Officer at Analyst Analyst IMS Investment Management Services Ltd since August 15, 2009. Mr. Shenidovski has a Bachelors degree in Business Management from Michlala Leminhal and a Masters degree in Business Management from Ben Gurion University.




							Nava Levi


					
							Ms. Nava Levi serves as Chief Financial Officer at Analyst IMS Investment Management Services Ltd since January 06, 2003. Ms. Levi studied at the College of Management, Israel.




							Ofer Lotan


					
							Mr. Ofer Lotan has been named Chief Executive Officer of Analyst Portfolio Management Ltd., a subsidiary of Analyst IMS Investment Management Services Ltd. effective June 1, 2014. Prior to this role, Mr. Lotan has served as Portfolio Manager at Analyst IMS Investment Management Services Ltd. from 2008, a role he still holds. Prior to that, he served as Director at Analyst Provident Funds Ltd. from July, 2013, a role he still holds. Mr. Lotan holds a Bachelors degree in Economics and Business Administration from The Hebrew University of Jerusalem and a MBA degree from Haifa University.




							Tzur Peleg


					
							Mr. Tzur Peleg serves as Chief Executive Officer of Analyst Exchange Services & Trade Ltd., a subsidiary of Analyst IMS Investment Management Services Ltd., since March 1, 2010. Previously, he served as Senior Vice President of Clal Finance Betucha (Clal), prior to this as branch manager of Clal and prior to this as Financial Advisor for Clal. Mr. Peleg holds a Bachelors degree in Business Administration from The College of Management, Israel, and an MBA from the University of Manchester.




							Ilana Primo


					
							Ms. Ilana Primo serves as Chief Executive Officer for Analyst Funds Ltd., a subsidiary of Analyst IMS Investment Management Services Ltd. since February 1, 2000. Ms. Primo holds a Bachelors degree in Chemistry and Bachelors degree in Business Management, both from Bar-Ilan University.




							Alon Agoshbitz


					
							Mr. Alon Agoshbitz serves as Chief Operating Officer at Analyst IMS Investment Management Services Ltd since January 30, 2012. Previously, he served as CEO of Analyst IMS Trust Funds (1986), a subsidiary of the Company, from December 25, 2002 until January 30, 2012. Mr. Agoshbitz holds a Bachelors degree in Computer Science, a Bachelors degree in Mathematics and a Masters degree in Business Administration, all from the Tel Aviv University.




