							Ms. Michal Hacker serves as General Counsel at Analyst IMS Investment Management Services Ltd since May 1, 2011. Previously, she served as an Attorney for Caspi & Assoc. for over 10 years. Ms. Hacker holds an LLB and a LLM from Bar-Ilan University.




